fragment_downloaded_cb({"url": "gtkgrid-h.html#gtk_grid_attach_next_to", "fragment": "Gtk.Grid.AttachNextTo \nAdds a widget to the grid. \nThe widget is placed next to sibling on the side determined by side. When sibling is null the widget is placed in row for left or right placement or column for top or bottom placement at the end indicated by side. \nAttaching widgets labeled with sibling null and side Gtk.PositionType.Left yields a layout of \nParameters \nthe widget to add \nthe child of grid that child will be placed next to or null to place child at the beginning or end \nthe side of sibling that child is positioned next to \nthe number of columns that child will span \nthe number of rows that child will span \n"});